    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Negative Energy is a tower defense game with basic RTS mechanics, where your goal is to defend the construction of a Dyson sphere until it ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build ships, assign them to fleets and strategically move them within the perimeter of the star system to intercept and destroy enemy fleets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Note:</u></strong><u> Some game mechanics are not yet listed here. Please refer to the Early Access Section to view all the upcoming implementations, that may or may not be already  implemented.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build ships and assign them to fleets;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/f8cb56b0b176a43dcd54886f42af8aea.poster.avif?t=1744915282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/f8cb56b0b176a43dcd54886f42af8aea.webm?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/f8cb56b0b176a43dcd54886f42af8aea.mp4?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan fleets timing and intercept positions in the most efficient way to counter enemy attacks;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/925c3228c5746757f7d66615a8c3444a.poster.avif?t=1744915282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/925c3228c5746757f7d66615a8c3444a.webm?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/925c3228c5746757f7d66615a8c3444a.mp4?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack and move your ships to gain the initiative;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/ded0bca6724218874a97b1c08ad2b056.poster.avif?t=1744915282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/ded0bca6724218874a97b1c08ad2b056.webm?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/ded0bca6724218874a97b1c08ad2b056.mp4?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reassign ships to another fleets;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/94d6de69514fd7a036098886e5a9dcd2.poster.avif?t=1744915282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/94d6de69514fd7a036098886e5a9dcd2.webm?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002720/extras/94d6de69514fd7a036098886e5a9dcd2.mp4?t=1744915282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage and gather the available resources to build better ships;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pause the game at any given time;</p></li></ul>",
